rent, to pronounced proximity junction behavior\nat large positive gate voltage, with enhanced Josephson current and subgap\nconductance as well as a large positive excess current.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Nov 2013 17:05:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Nov 2013 10:40:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 27 Jun 2014 12:13:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-02"}
