ing) Laplacian operators,\nFrequency Variogram, Tests for independence, Whittle likelihood.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Nov 2013 14:23:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Dec 2015 20:20:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-31"}
